\SE[76]Phew... Finally finished. \!\SE[51]From military exercises
to budget management and diplomatic issues.... \!\SE[75]Even if
things become somewhat peaceful, these \SM[nod]tasks never seem
to decrease at all....
\SE[51]Hmm... Maybe I should take a little break...

\SE[94] (Gah, Nikita...? \SE[59] I have a bad feeling about
this...)

Oh, welcome. I was surprised because you came earlier than
planned.

I'm a capable woman, you know. I easily took care of those
miscellaneous tasks.

Wow... As expected, you're really efficient. I should learn from
you a little. Oh, since we're already chatting, do you want to
come to my room? Tita just prepared some snacks.
Oh my, oh my...? \!It seems like I came at a good time.

\SM[nod]\SE[2]Phew... My heart can't take it.... So you had a
promise over there.

\SE[66]...It's only natural for me to have something to do here,
it's not like I'm being conceited or anything...\!\SM[nod]\SE[84]
Sigh...

\SE[74] (I wonder if Nikita and Lunaroa have that kind of
relationship...)

\SE[2] (No, that's not possible. \!\SE[51]Lunaroa is determined,
after all...)

\SE[94]Ugh! It seems troublesome to face each other...!
\SE[91]\SM[pop]Let's just progress with the work a little
longer...!

\SE[79]\SM[nod]Hmm... It's progressing more smoothly than I
expected. \SE[2]I think I've managed to free up quite a bit of
time, so I can keep an eye on those girls for a while.

Thank you for the meal... Ah, it was delicious.... I have to
thank Tita, but if I don't do some exercise, it won't be good....

Hehe, it's a troublesome problem. I can't waste that child's
affection, so every day is a battle with desires.
So, about that... \!The thing you asked for...\.Can I go get it?

...Yes, it's fine. \!I've made some improvements compared to
before, so even if you're not used to it, you should be able to
handle it.

As expected of a pro in that field. Consulting with you was the
right decision. I'm sure you're feeling tired in a good way right
now...

Yes, it's a success... I'll pray for good luck. \!...Do your
best!

\SE[24]Vega-chan, help me!! \!\SE[52]\\SM[double]Lunaroa's magic
went out of control, and now I have a penis growing on me!!

\SE[22]I heard everything!! \SE[19]What is this!? That childish
lie...!?

\SE[51]Oh no... I've been found out. \SE[20]I've been trying to
cover things up, but it's embarrassing, big sister...

\SE\SE[45]If that's the case... there's no point in pretending to
be strangers now. \.I wanted to handle this more gracefully,
but... \.\SE[0]It can't be helped. \!\SE[45]Vega-chan. \.Let me
embrace you.

\SE[74]You're quite curious, aren't you... \SE[51]There are
probably plenty of better people than me for you, right?

\SE[6]I wonder how to put it... \SE[15]The strong-willed aura of
Vega-chan, it really pierces right into my heart...

\SE[31]I want to support you. I want to be there for you. I want
to embrace the weakness that you carry... \SE[5]Those are the
kind of feelings that I have...
\SE[74].........I didn't ask for something like that, you know?

\SE[29]Even this inability to be honest...! It's like saying
Please conquer me!...? \SE[58]\SM[slidef]Right now, I can't
resist the urge to kiss you.

\SE[83] (You're sober, right...? I wonder if there's alcohol in
these sweets.)

\SE[44]But, I can't...\.hold back anymore.
\!\SM[tremble]\SE[58]Maybe it's because of my growth...\.I can't
control myself. \!\SE[59]I can't bear to restrain myself today.
Hey...! I also need to prepare myself mentally...!!
